&lt;li&gt;A strong communicator who can articulate technical direction across engineering teams and external partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Someone with deep knowledge of safety-critical systems and the unique needs of automotive environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An innovator who can identify future use cases and propose next-generation architectural solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A leader who thrives in a highly technical, cross-functional, fast-moving environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Need&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
