&lt;li&gt;Proven track record in pipeline development, client relationship management, and closing commercial opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with cross-border teams and managing multi-stakeholder initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in English is required.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
