&lt;li&gt;Building a regional network while collaborating with global BD, product, and technical teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deeper expertise in market analysis, sales operations, and deal execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
