&lt;li&gt;Effective collaboration across global teams and external partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How Tenstorrent evolves and standardizes physical design methodologies across projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
